{Justin and Roland were two ordinary fixers in the backstreets, exhausted by the everyday stresses of the City. One day, they left their jobs and prepared to go to the bar and have a good time. Justin was happy, having recently been promoted to a grade 3 fixer, and Roland was just happy to be in the company of his friend. The two drank and spoke about the struggles in their lives. But... the bar, it's... a bit hot...}
